Thanks, works fine.

1. The contents does not need to be extracted. Just mount with DAEMON Tools, then follow the instructions.

2. Serial: Goto 'My Computer', right-click and Open 'FIFA07'. Goto the 'Crack' folder and open 'rld-f07k.exe', then click 'Generate' so generate a serial.

3. Crack: Goto 'My Computer', right-click and Open 'FIFA07'. Goto the 'Crack' folder and double-click 'fifa07.exe', and Fifa should start.

4. Language selection: Select your language, then press Enter on your keyboard.

hei hva betyr og seeda ???

Seed: a peer who has 100% of the torrent and is only uploading to other peers. Seed is also used as a verb, as in "I'm going to be seeding this file overnight", meaning leave open and available for other users to download. Usually, a person with the whole file is a 'seed', while someone with a partial amount is a peer. Remember that a seed is not a file server. We're not talking about "magic seeds" here, so get any idea like that out of your mind. Connecting to more seeds does not necessarily mean that you'll finish downloading any faster. If you don't connect to all the seeds in a swarm, or even if you don't connect to any seeds, it does not mean Azureus is doing anything wrong. For any random torrent, you might download faster when connected only to 5 other peers and no seeds than you might with some other random torrent while connected to 50 seeds and no other peers. Seeding torrents improves your Share Ratio.
